  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h2>
<p>You can also import the Expertflow Live Chat template from Github Repository, In case you don’t find it in the Community Gallery of Tag Manager.</p>
<p>Import from GitHub Repository</p>
<ol>
 <li>
  <p>Download the Tag templates source code from</p>
  <a href="https://github.com/expertflow/expertflow-cim-tag-template" data-scope="external" rel="external noreferrer">
   <p>here</p>
  </a>
  <p>.
   <br></p>
 </li>
 <li>
