  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h2>
<p>The Additional Panel on the web widget is coming from the index.html file.</p>
<p><span class="theme-inline-image"> <image-lightbox> <span class="inline-image" data-component="inline-image" data-use-text-height="false" style="--height: 250px;"> <img src="/__attachments/a_7ede17e8f5279f39abb271a4769d646ea5561de718e344c889a309d1e678bfe1/image2022-5-9_14-20-5.png?cb=ab0a2d111ac66c2b9559de3306469ff2" alt="image2022-5-9_14-20-5.png" data-scope="internal"> </span> </image-lightbox> </span></p>
<p>one can use the Additional Panel by uncommenting the HTML code from&nbsp;the <strong>index.html</strong> file.
 <br>
 <span class="theme-inline-image"> <image-lightbox> <span class="inline-image" data-component="inline-image" data-use-text-height="false" style="--height: 250px;"> <img src="/__attachments/a_2d86777b5305db0ca5a60226b5ba94a0ec4982ce07fe44766cb1abba752e1de7/image2022-5-9_14-18-41.png?cb=ffe58ea40ca947e45be6d5926fdf7588" alt="image2022-5-9_14-18-41.png" data-scope="internal"> </span> </image-lightbox> </span></p>
<p>If an Additional Panel is not required then just comment on the HTML code.</p>

